Hey fellow users we are really happy to release our Fill feature!! You are now able to replace any shape or sticker with your own picture or color while keeping the original shape! A world of possibilities is waiting for you!

Create beautiful content with the 100s of templates available and editable in just one tap! Home work party black white vintage everything you need to shine on your social networks is on the app In this version we have also improved our automatic background removal to bring your ideas to life in no time. We hope you enjoy this version!

Introducing our brand new version with thousands of stickers! The new layer management will give you both space to work on the details of your design and all the options to manage the order of your layers. We look forward to your feedback! Happy editing!

New features that make your next photo montage easier. Add corner radius to your images or shapes. Hide lock or duplicate the layers you want to. Choose a color from millions or take a color present in one of your photos. Long press on an image to see before and after adding an effect. New adjustments: Vignette sharpness.

PROJECT FORMAT Start a project by choosing the format of your favorite social network or define a custom size. CLIPPING We have improved the clipping functionality use it with all your portrait photos.

SAVE PROJECT With this version you can SAVE your project. Yes you read it correctly! You are working for a long time on your masterpiece and feeling tired Save it and finish it later with all your changes stil available. NEW FILTERS We ve added brand new effects like Glitch Duotone Plastic and many more to discover. Try them all and transform any picture into a piece of art!
